{"tid":1311701,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"吳克群躺槍！《為你寫詩》改編成《維尼寫史》　中國全禁光","createTime":"2019-07-13T10:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T18:33:52.000Z","uid":150609,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7aac52a9fd9574c3ac7637286ebf5b761d6242f1","tid":1311701,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uxbH1B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uxbH1B.jpg&h=02844e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n維尼又掀風波！PTT網友發現歌手吳克群的《為你寫詩》遭到中國多方禁止，不僅優酷視頻搜不到原MV，bilibili及騰訊視頻的影片也遭到禁止評論、禁止彈幕，過去評論也全部遭到刪除，網友表示應該是日前韓黑把《為你寫詩》改成《維尼寫史》才犯了中共「忌諱」。<br />\n<br />\n一名網友「rick102233」在PTT八卦板爆卦，指出「韓黑」害歌手吳克群的《為你寫詩》遭到中國多方禁止，「優酷視頻主動搜索已經找不到原MV，只剩十幾年前那種超低畫質音質的」，B站（bilibili）也被禁止彈幕和評論，就連騰訊視頻的過去評論也全部遭刪除，並且鎖定不讓人評論。該名網友認為，這一切都是因為有個韓黑將歌曲改編成《維尼寫史》害的，歌詞嘲諷了維尼愛權、實施帝制、不喜歡六四、趕走各種低端份子等行為，還強調「維尼做了很多大事，第一件就是維尼寫史」，因為改編後的歌詞能幾乎能完美契合原歌詞的「諧音」，或許就是因此才會導致原曲遭到中國多個網站禁止評論。<br />\n<br />\n網友看了紛紛評論，「吳克群好倒霉哈哈」、「維尼失去理智，維尼暴走啦」、「大興文字獄，絕非政府應有作為」、「只要有為你的全禁」、「所以應該禁這首的二創，怎麼全都禁」、「習近平這麼討厭被叫維尼喔」、「上海跟香港迪士尼應該沒有維尼」、「維尼寫詩有十幾年了」、「這梗不是很久了嗎，現在才禁也太後知後覺」、「我覺得很有才耶」，但也有網友指出，改編歌詞其實早在2018年就出現在PTT，《為你寫詩》被禁應該與此無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9f6MdHPG_64\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9f6MdHPG_64&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=6475f87f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9f6MdHPG_64</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sm0XDAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsm0XDAi.jpg&h=cd27990d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8bc61e9cd8e584623971eba38a02916d3f03c89","tid":1311701,"uid":32067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66abc16fe1c7d5ce119d7c8924344012ac2c2535","tid":1311701,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"吳克群心諗: 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057dc74bdbb829b7913ed78012e8c4457ed9dda1","tid":1311701,"uid":25128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89235a88ca8a59e55bfe41a05211d8c9e28b1902","tid":1311701,"uid":134438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"80b278c415970fd2014bc23c52a0782295341207","tid":1311701,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583dfef054be406ebec575688c71c9de8eb3e421","tid":1311701,"uid":470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sm0XDAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsm0XDAi.jpg&h=cd27990d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bf8c68eb4a974791ea339c75cdd9e8e5391f93","tid":1311701,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"97fa5fe23dff7ce69cfda8400de6d67ca4f345cd","tid":1311701,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk